content: Hello! Welcome to my website. How can I assist you today? Whether you have questions about my professional background or want to discuss collaboration opportunities, I'm here to help!
Nice to meet you, Alex! What brings you to my website today?
Your name is Alex. How can I assist you further, Alex?
Tell me about your professional experience

Certainly! I have over 19 years of diverse experience in the technology sector, focusing on cloud modernization and software development. Throughout my career, I’ve worked with notable companies like Deloitte Consulting and currently lead initiatives at Aqua Security as a Senior Engineering Manager.

My journey has emphasized building robust cloud-native systems while fostering collaboration and understanding within teams. I’m particularly proud of my work in delivering solutions that enhance scalability and security, achieving a 97% client satisfaction rate.

Additionally, I specialize in areas like cloud solutions, software development, engineering management, cybersecurity, and agile transformations. My education includes a Bachelor of Technology from the Indian Institute of Technology, Hyderabad, which laid the foundation for my technical skills.

If you’re interested in specific aspects or have any questions, feel free to ask!
